    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super careful with it\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like a total dream and has been babied since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
