    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a finish that is virtually indistinguishable from new. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, further enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, free of any bolster wear or creasing, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service portfolio with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This sale includes the original window sticker, all sets of keys, and a full set of owner\u2019s manuals. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example currently on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
